OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,FA lack of clinical NHS support, as
OL,7,Fwell as a lengthy criminal
OL,8,Finvestigation into allegations against
OL,9,Fhim contributed to the death of a
OL,10,FCumbria Police officer who took his
OL,11,Fown life, an inquest has concluded.
OL,13,FJames Thistlethwaite was found dead at
OL,14,Fhis home in Keswick on 19 August 2023
OL,15,Fat the age of 44. He had served as a
OL,16,Fpolice officer for 17 years.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,FIn October 2022 Mr Thistlethwaite was
OL,7,Fsuspended from his role as a police
OL,8,Fofficer after an allegation was made
OL,9,Fagainst him of sexual assault towards
OL,10,Fa woman referred to as Miss A.
OL,12,FConcluding an inquest into his death
OL,13,Fat HM Coroner's Court in Workington,
OL,14,FCoroner Robert Cohen said: "It is more
OL,15,Flikely than not that the protracted
OL,16,Fnature of the criminal investigation,
OL,17,Fand the absence of more frequent
OL,18,Fclinical contact between 14 and 18
OL,19,FAugust 2023, each contributed to Mr
OL,20,FThistlethwaite's death."
OL,26,@vD@\OU|D@XO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,FMr Cohen concluded the cause of death
OL,7,Fwas suicide.
OL,9,FMr Thistlethwaite's wife, Jennifer,
OL,10,Fhad told the inquest his job as a
OL,11,Fpolice officer caused him to suffer
OL,12,Ffrom PTSD.
OL,14,FShe said his mental health never
OL,15,Frecovered after he went to a call out
OL,16,Fin October 2021 where a baby died.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,FMrs Thistlethwaite told the court she
OL,7,Fbelieved the prolonged investigation
OL,8,Finto the alleged sexual assault along
OL,9,Fwith NHS failings led to her husband's
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FThe court heard he was referred to a
OL,13,Fmental health crisis house in July
OL,14,F2023, and was discharged on 6 August
OL,15,Fbut then referred to the crisis house
OL,16,Fagain on 9 August.
OL,18,FOn 12 August Mr Thistlethwaite was
OL,19,Fdischarged again, and less than one
OL,20,Fweek later on 19 August he was found
OL,21,Fdead at his home in Keswick.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,FThe inquest heard the last face-to-
OL,7,Fface risk assessment characterised him
OL,8,Fas having a "significant risk of
OL,9,Fsuicide."
OL,11,FElaine Fletcher, Director of Nursing
OL,12,Fat Cumbria, Northumberland, Tyne and
OL,13,FWear NHS Foundation Trust said this
OL,14,Fwas not the most serious level of
OL,15,Frisk, and said: "The assessment at the
OL,16,Ftime was that he was well enough to go
OL,17,Fhome, to keep himself safe, and to be
OL,18,Fseen by clinicians thereafter."
OL,26,@pD@MOUqD@IO]wD@QOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,FMr Cohen said that when Mr
OL,7,FThistlethwaite was transferred from
OL,8,Fthe Crisis Team to the Community
OL,9,FTreatment Team, "the plan had been
OL,10,Fthat James should be seen twice a day,
OL,11,Fand this did not happen."
OL,13,FMs Fletcher told the inquest she
OL,14,Fbelieved communication between the
OL,15,Fdifferent teams involved in James's
OL,16,Fcare could have been better.
OL,26,@qD@QOUsD@YO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,FShe added that supervision for
OL,7,Fclinicians has been improved and that
OL,8,Frisk assessments are now categorised
OL,9,Fin a more holistic way, with records
OL,10,Fbetter kept on a more central
OL,11,Fdashboard.
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Simon Gray of
OL,14,FCumbra Police was investigating the
OL,15,Fallegation made against Mr
OL,16,FThistlethwaite of sexual assault
OL,17,Ftowards 'Miss A.'
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,FHe told the inquest he attempted to
OL,7,Fspeed up the investigation, knowing
OL,8,Fthe amount of time it was taking was
OL,9,Fhaving an impact of his mental state.
OL,10,FHowever he said a key potential
OL,11,Fwitness to the alleged sexual assault
OL,12,Fwas living overseas at the time,
OL,13,Fleading to a lengthy wait to get a
OL,14,Fwitness statement.
OL,16,FSumming up, Coroner Cohen told the
OL,17,Fcourt: "Serious allegations were made
OL,18,Fagainst James and it was right that
OL,19,Fthey were investigated."
OL,26,@yD@HOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,FMr Cohen said he did not believe
OL,7,FCumbria Police failed to take
OL,8,Freasonable steps to alleviate any risk
OL,9,Fto Mr Thistlethwaite, and that his
OL,10,Fsuspension "did not cause or
OL,11,Fcontribute to his death"
OL,13,FHe added: "No investigation should
OL,14,Fdisregard the effect it may have on
OL,15,Fthe person being investigated, but
OL,16,Fthat does not mean an investigation
OL,17,Fshould stop simply because of the
OL,18,Fimpact it is having on that person."
OL,26,@rD@LOUsD@XO]uD@KOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,FIn a statement, Jennifer
OL,7,FThistlethwaite and the family said:
OL,8,F"James was a deeply loved husband,
OL,9,Ffather, son, brother, uncle and friend
OL,10,Fwhose warmth, kindness, and spirit
OL,11,Ftouched the lives of everyone who knew
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,F"He brought so much light into our
OL,15,Flives, and that is how we will always
OL,16,Fchoose to remember him.
OL,26,@pD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1780596668
OL,3,CCumbria Police officer died by
OL,4,Csuicide, coroner's inquest finds
OL,6,F"While we now have the coroner's
OL,7,Fformal findings regarding James's
OL,8,Ftragic passing by suicide,
OL,9,Funderstanding them does not make the
OL,10,Freality of his absence any easier to
OL,11,Fbear.
OL,13,F"This conclusion brings a painful kind
OL,14,Fof closure, but it also reopens the
OL,15,Fdeep wounds of our grief."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
